{{lang|en|'''Rockstar Games Social Club'''}}（'''RGSC'''）是[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]]推出的包含[[数字版权管理|数字版权管理]]、[[多人電子遊戲|多人電子遊戲]]和[[社交網絡服務|社交網絡]]功能於一身的服務平台，最初於2008年3月27日公佈<ref>{{cite web| title = Rockstar {{sic|nolink=y|Annonunces|expected=Announces}} Social Club| work = RockstarWatch| publisher = RockstarWatch| date = 2008-08-01| url = http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/357/Rockstar-Annonunces-Social-Club/| accessdate = 2008-03-27| archive-date = 2008-04-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080403001446/http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/357/Rockstar-Annonunces-Social-Club/| dead-url = no}}</ref>，並在4月14日開始預先註冊。<ref>{{cite web| title = Rockstar Social Club: Pre-Registration Delayed| work = RockstarWatch| publisher = RockstarWatch| date = 2008-08-01| url = http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/401/Rockstar-Social-Club-Pre-Registration-Delayed/| accessdate = 2008-04-14| archive-date = 2008-05-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080503222726/http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/401/Rockstar-Social-Club-Pre-Registration-Delayed/| dead-url = no}}</ref>不過，註冊要到4月17日才開始進行。<ref>{{cite web| title = Rockstar Social Club Registration Opens Today| work = RockstarWatch| publisher = RockstarWatch| date = 2008-04-17| url = http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/422/Rockstar-Social-Club-Registration-Opens-Today/| accessdate = 2008-04-17| archive-date = 2008-05-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080503222730/http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/422/Rockstar-Social-Club-Registration-Opens-Today/| dead-url = no}}</ref>「Social Club」這個名字來源於[[黑社會|黑社會]]，他們經常會使用這個詞來指代他們的會面地點或藏身之處。在2012年Rcokstar Games發布[[江湖本色3|江湖本色3]]之前，平台進行了一次重大升級。這次升級除了增加了社交網絡服務外，還增加了「幫會」（Crews）系統。註冊玩家可以建立或加入一個幫會，組成隊伍與其他隊伍進行較量，同時獲取聲望值或經驗值的獎勵。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5908510/rockstar-games-social-club-just-got-a-lot-more-social |title=Rockstar Games' Social Club Just Got a Lot More Social |publisher=Kotaku.com |date=2012-05-08 |accessdate=2012-10-18 |archive-date=2012-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120809143029/http://kotaku.com/5908510/rockstar-games-social-club-just-got-a-lot-more-social |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/33771/introducing-the-allnew-rockstar-games-social-club.html |title=Introducing the All-New Rockstar Games Social Club |publisher=Rockstar Games |date=2012-05-07 |accessdate=2012-10-18 |archive-date=2013-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420122501/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/33771/introducing-the-allnew-rockstar-games-social-club.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RGSCCrews_zh">{{cite web |url=http://zh.socialclub.rockstargames.com/crews |title=Rockstar Games Social Club - Crews : Community |publisher=Rockstar Games |accessdate=2014-03-27 |language=zh |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131018023522/http://zh.socialclub.rockstargames.com/crews |archive-date=2013-10-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="RGSCAbout_zh">{{cite web |url=http://zh.socialclub.rockstargames.com/about |title=Rockstar Games Social Club - About |publisher=Rockstar Games |accessdate=2014-03-27 |language=zh }}{{Dead link|date=2019年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

== 特色內容 ==
Rockstar Games Social Club會記錄會員的遊戲數據，對數據進行追蹤。它提供了遊戲導覽功能，不但能記錄玩家遊戲進度，也會給予玩家遊戲提示。Social Club包含有社交網絡的服務，通過遊戲中社群和幫會系統，前者能夠使會員之間進行互相交流，後者可讓會員組成隊伍在遊戲中進行較量。註冊成為Social Club會員後，玩家會獲得專屬的遊戲內容，並能參加「Social Club挑戰」以及官方定期舉辦的遊戲和抽獎贈送活動。<ref name="RGSCAbout_zh"/>

== 支援遊戲 ==
截至2021年，以下遊戲中包含有Rockstar Games Social Club平台<ref>{{cite web |url=http://socialclub.rockstargames.com/games/ |title=Rockstar Games Social Club - Games |publisher=Rockstar Games |accessdate=9 July 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130708144818/http://socialclub.rockstargames.com/games |archive-date=2013-07-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。目前，幫會系統只支持[[江湖本色3|江湖本色3]]、[[俠盜獵車手V|俠盜獵車手V]]及其之後發布的遊戲<ref name="RGSCCrews_zh"/>。
